├── Co-op Bridge           — requires BOTH shards activated to lower
├── Final Platform        (Z=+200) — Exit trigger
└── Lighting:
    - DynamicLightSource_01 (Stationary PointLight, warm)
    - DynamicLightSource_02 (Stationary PointLight, cool)
